results.title: Blind Ambition!
results.description: The Thing battles the Rekoner on The Secret Wars Planet.

results.title: Family Man
results.description: The Thing and Tarianna return Juneyar, the rightful king of Muab, to his city.

items.name: Fantastic Four Visionaries: John Byrne Vol. 5 (2005)
Fantastic Four Visionaries: John Byrne Vol. 5 (Trade Paperback)

results.title: Monster Mash
results.description: The Thing battles various monsters on The Secret Wars Planet.

items.name: Fantastic Four Visionaries: John Byrne Vol. 5 (2005)
Fantastic Four Visionaries: John Byrne Vol. 5 (Trade Paperback)

results.title: For Beauty Passed Away
results.description: The Thing visits his girlfriend Alicia Masters in the hospital and tells her about his college love, Alynn Cambers.

items.name: Fantastic Four Visionaries: John Byrne Vol. 3 (2004)
Fantastic Four Visionaries: John Byrne Vol. 3 (Trade Paperback)

results.title: The Way Things Were
results.description: The Thing battles Tarianna inside her mind.  Ultron is reborn.

results.title: Revelations!
results.description: The Thing battles a duplicate Ben Grimm on The Secret Wars Planet.

results.title: To All Things An Ending
results.description: The Thing confronts and defeats his double on The Secret Wars Planet.  After losing Tarianna, he returns to Earth.

items.name: Fantastic Four Visionaries: John Byrne Vol. 6 (2006)
Fantastic Four Visionaries: John Byrne Vol. 6 (Trade Paperback)

results.title: Remembrances
results.description: The Thing quits the Fantastic Four.

items.name: Fantastic Four Visionaries: John Byrne Vol. 6 (2006)
Fantastic Four Visionaries: John Byrne Vol. 6 (Trade Paperback)

results.title: One Man's Prison
results.description: The Thing battles The Rhino whose mind is being controlled by The Miracle Man.

results.title: Legends
results.description: The Thing is granted three wishes by a group of Leprechauns.

results.title: Runaways
results.description: The Thing and Vance Astrovik battle The Taskmaster at the circus.

results.title: The Thing and The Thunderiders
results.description: The Thing and Vance Astrovik battle the Black Marauder.  The Thing joins The Thunderiders.

results.title: In This Corner
results.description: The Thing leaves The Thunderiders and joins The Unlimited Class Wrestling Federation.

results.title: The Thing vs. Gator
results.description: The Thing wrestles one-time champ, Gator Grant.

results.title: Turning Point
results.description: The Thing helps Crystal save Luna, her human son, from being exposed to the Inhumans' Terragen Mist which might endow him with Inhuman powers.

results.title: Above and Beyond
results.description: The Thing Wrestles The Beyonder in the Unlimited Class Wrestling Federation.

results.title: Devil Dinosaur:  The Movie
results.description: The Thing battles a robot Devil Dinosaur.

results.title: Home
results.description: The Thing saves an out-of-control airplane.  Vance Astrovik returns to his parents.

results.title: Battle of the Sexes
results.description: The Thing wrestles Battleaxe, as well as the rest of The New Grapplers

results.title: Dual Duel
results.description: The Thing battles The Sphinx with the help of The Puppet Master

results.title: Power Play!
results.description: Sharon Ventura is transformed into Ms. Marvel II.

results.title: Going for Broke
results.description: The She-Hulk battles the new Ms. Marvel.  The Thing is mutated into a monster.

results.title: I, Monster
results.description: The Thing and Lockjaw help Sarah Ann Jackson and her son Lucas against a small town's prejudice.

results.title: With Friends Like These ...
results.description: The Thing battles Wonder Man, She Hulk, and Spider-Man, who are being controlled by the Puppet Master

results.title: Mindscape
results.description: The Thing battles the Puppet Master inside the Thing's mind.

results.title: Two-Fisted Feet
results.description: The Thing fights an overrated Goody Two Shoes.

results.title: What Th' ?!
results.description: The Thing confronts his artists about the first story.

results.title: Ancient Evenings Ancient Pain
results.description: The Thing has his body inhabited by an egyptian slave who wants a 4000 year-old revenge.

results.title: What Price A Soul?
results.description: A mind-controlled Thing rampages in New York.  The love of his girlfriend, Alicia, saves him.

results.title: Beware the Claws of the Cat
From Far Beneath the Mirror of the Moon
The Female of the Species
results.description: explanation of Marvel Girl's powers
